title: SIP-009 Enabling gOHM-FTM bond
body:
Background:

gOHM is the cross-chain, wrapped sOHM.

gOHM will be on Fantom network soon. Spartacus DAO will be proud to be the first to support gOHM-FTM bond on Fantom. 

Enabling gOHM-FTM bond will add gOHM assets into Spartacus Treasury, helping integrating SPA into the Olympus DAO system and open Spartacus to a much broader community. 

This is part of our initiative to work closely with OlympusDAO team. 

Olympus DAO will be incentivizing the gOHM-FTM pool. Accepting gOHM-FTM bonds allows Spartacus Treasury to receive farming rewards of OHM as well. This is a win-win for Spartacus and Olympus DAO.

Proposal: Enable bonding with gOHM-FTM LP to receive SPA token. 

Please vote to support this initiative. 

Yea - for the proposal
Nay - against the proposal
author: 0x547991a0FCc6dCA62734FeDAbA5901faF717706a
